data.description: Very desirable Section 15, 3/2/2, 2133sf, BEAUTIFUL pool home in a non deed restricted community with city water and sewer.  This won't last long! Walking through the double door entry you will have a great view of the pool and outdoor living space just beyond the living room. The dining room allows lots of natural light in from the oversized window that looks north across the front yard. There are high ceilings throughout the home, ceiling fans in most rooms and a split floor plan that offers privacy from the master bedroom side of the home. The updated kitchen looks into the great room and has a view of the lanai/pool area. There is an island for additional counter/work space and additional storage, cooktop, quartz counter tops and beautiful solid maple wood cabinets with many roll outs. The home is decorated in neutral tones and has Italian porcelain tile in the main living areas of the home and carpet in the bedrooms. The spacious great room is located in the rear of the home and has access to the lanai with a bay window overlooking the backyard. The huge master bedroom has plenty of space for a sitting/office/workout area, sliders out to the lanai with a nice view of the pool, and 2 walk in closets. The master bathroom has a separate walk-in shower and  tub, a water closet and separate dual sinks with lots of storage. The 2nd and third bedrooms are across the house. They both have walk-in closets and are bright comfortable rooms. The guest bathroom has a shower/tub, single sink, and a skylight. The outdoor living space has shade under roof as well as under screen (37x22ft) to enjoy outdoor living. Sit back and relax or go for a float in your private, solar heated pool. There is a shed and the yard is fenced. This home is located in a very desirable, friendly, well maintained neighborhood. Make an appointment soon, it will not last long!
